    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s in pristine, flawless condition inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel and a totally spotless ride, this is the one you've been waiting for! It runs like a dream and looks even better in person. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 47900.0,
