    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presenting in a state that rivals its original delivery day. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating, completely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the alloy wheels are flawless, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the leather seats show no signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car has been pampered with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy, documented by a complete set of service records from the original dealership. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the low mileage and climate-controlled garage storage this vehicle has enjoyed since day one. This is not just a used car; it is an investment-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
