      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
